  "remarks": "Former Speaker of the Russian Duma.  Member of the National Security Council and of the United Russia Party.  Publicly supported the deployment of Russian forces in Ukraine.  Publicly supported the Russia-Crimea reunification treaty and the related federal constitutional law.  Head of the Foreign Intelligence Service of the Russian Federation since October 2016.  Permanent member of the Security Council of the Russian Federation; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (re-listed on 16 Jun. 2017, 10 June 2020 and 10 June 2023)",
